data.description: This conveniently positioned home near popular amenities will delight you. Bask in the ample natural light that fills the spacious, open living area, while the kitchen flows effortlessly and offers ample storage space. Neutral, comforting hues are found throughout this extensively remodeled home. All bedrooms are spacious and inviting, plus you'll love the bonus room that could be your very own home office space. When it's time to relax after a long day, you'll love sipping your favorite beverage from the comfort of your covered back patio that looks out to your large backyard, complete with a storage shed for all of your outdoor necessities. Experience this gem for yourself today!
